MWP Framework 2.0 Breaking Changes
--------------------

- Class namespacing has been changed from Modern\Wordpress to MWP\Framework
- Hooks:
  modern_wordpress_init => mwp_framework_init
  modern_wordpress_find_plugins => mwp_framework_plugins
  modern_wordpress_queue_run => mwp_framework_queue_run
  modern_wordpress_queue_maintenance => mwp_framework_queue_maintenance
- Constant MODERN_WORDPRESS_DEV changed to MWP_FRAMEWORK_DEBUG
- Class ModernWordpressFramework => MWPFramework